{"tid":2166210,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"UGL醜聞 林卓廷：企硬告689","createTime":"2020-08-20T09:47:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-20T09:50:47.000Z","uid":25558,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"4f23ae15d22957969649f7f32bdcb32416453338","tid":2166210,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-20T09:47:45.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200820/7ZC6BJIKFJDBBDUQJ4E536M3AM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200820%2F7ZC6BJIKFJDBBDUQJ4E536M3AM%2F&d=hRZI3RxrLdWDWG%2FiPctn5cWiAETkOtN%2FvKUl8N5Dwlc%3D&h=4cabb6a9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200820%2F7ZC6BJIKFJDBBDUQJ4E536M3AM%2F&h=db473f67\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200820/7ZC6BJIKFJDBBDUQJ4E536M3AM/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\nUGL醜聞 林卓廷：企硬告689<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/_P1G3-bRA_vuCBZRx6XuCzn5XRY=/1329x886/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/FH5VRTG3MRAWLHWU7WHK2NN7BE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F_P1G3-bRA_vuCBZRx6XuCzn5XRY%3D%2F1329x886%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FFH5VRTG3MRAWLHWU7WHK2NN7BE.jpg&h=f79914b0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■林卓廷<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】律政司前日去信法庭，表明接手民主黨立法會議員許智峯向法庭申請私人刑事檢控，控告交通警長去年在西灣河開槍射傷少年案件，並豁免警長出庭。外界正關注律政司會否用相同手法，處理民主黨議員林卓廷擬就前特首梁振英收取UGL 5,000萬元一事提出的私人檢控，林卓廷表明即使律政司長鄭若驊或會介入案件，仍會堅持提出相關私人檢控。<br />\n<br />\n今次律政司介入許智峯對交通警長的私人刑事檢控，企圖放生有關警員，林卓廷批評，鄭若驊在法庭覺得有表面證據可以向開槍警長提出檢控下，仍然主動介入案件。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n斥律政司妨礙民間尋公義<br />\n<br />\n林卓廷指事件反映鄭若驊不但未有做好律政司工作，。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n早前「天下為公」發起眾籌、擬就前特首梁振英收取UGL 5,000萬元一事提出私人檢控，。。。。。。。。"},{"pid":"a43cf64518ef968f0b91680f895b2fe6a870cfae","tid":2166210,"uid":14494,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-20T09:50:47.000Z","msg":"大波驊：企硬撤銷傳票"}]}